import React from 'react'
import Head from './Head'
import Search from './Search'
import {BrowserRouter as Router,Switch,Route,Link} from "react-router-dom";

import "./Header.css"
import Navbar from './Navbar'
const Header = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
      <Head/>
        <Switch>
          <Route path="/about">
            <About />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/users">
            <Users />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/">
            <Home />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
    </Router>

    </>
  )
}

export default Header
